content: Hi Bill Strorbridge here. Please add my name to the texting channels. I would very much like to get started texting to help get the vote out. Thanks
Sorry. It's BILL STROBRIDGE. How do I start texting please

Hi Bill. I have added you to the Text Team channel here on DIscord, where you can find all things Text. In addition, I have included the link to sign up for Text Team training. Note that they do often have limited spots.(https://events.democrats.org/event/672393/)
Can you add me as well? I’m wanting to start texting asap!
Hi Val! Have you done a text training with us?
Not yet, I’m scheduled for one on Tuesday the tenth at 7p.m

Okay! Once you do your training the text team will tell you about its onboarding processes! But you won’t have access to those channels until after you’ve finished training and gone thru all the steps of onboarding.
Ok
thank you!
Thank you!
You’re welcome!

I’ll let you know if I have any further questions. I might because I found myself getting lost on where to go. I was supposed to be doing a phone bank now, but never received a link for it from it from Erin Lehman in my email
You should receive an email as well as a text from mobilize with the zoom link to join both our phone banks and our text bank trainings!
I get text to join the trainings, but only got this about the actual phone bank today
And I contacted the organizer and they said I would get an email from mobilize with a link to join the zoom meeting, but never got one
And I checked my spam and didn’t see it

I am so sorry that that happened to you! You may have turned off email notifications on your mobilize acct and that’s maybe why you didn’t get it. Can you try signing up for another phone bank rn and seeing if you get an email?
Thanks Alex. Did the training.
Yes, Hello. I've done the training. It's been more than 72 hours now. What's next please?
Bill we'll add you soon. We get you're excited.
We'll dm you soon with next steps.
Sorry I just got your message, I think I’m going to stick to text team. I have a virtual training tomorrow and next Thursday
Correct me if I’m wrong, did you say that after training people would be able to start there process with the text team?
Yes. We'll direct message you.
It would be bet if you update your display name to firstname lastname and state.
pls add me to the texting channel. already did the training.
That's not how it works.
Btw I just direct messaged you Edith.
